# Carbon Emission Analysis

Photo by Chris LeBoutillier (unsplash.com)

This report aims to analyze carbon emissions to examine the carbon footprint across various industries. We aim to identify sectors with the highest levels of emissions by analyzing them across countries and years, as well as to uncover trends.

Carbon emissions play a crucial role in the environment, accounting for over 75% of global emissions and posing a significant environmental challenge. These emissions contribute to the accumulation of greenhouse gases in the atmosphere, leading to climate change, planetary warming, and involvement in various environmental disasters.

Through this analysis, we hope to gain an understanding of the environmental impact of different industries and contribute to making informed decisions in sustainable development.

![](data:image/webp;base64,)

## Data Structure
The dataset consists of 4 tables containing information regarding carbon emissions generated during the production of goods.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

## Which products contribute the most to carbon emissions?
Top 10 góp phần nhiều nhất vào lượng khí thải carbon.

**SQL:**

GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 10;`

## What are the industry groups of these products?
Industry_group của các sản phẩm top 10 thải ra 

SQL:
`SELECT p.product_name, i.industry_group, sum(p.carbon_footprint_pcf) AS CO2_emissions
FROM product_emissions p
JOIN industry_groups i
ON p.industry_group_id = i.id
GROUP BY p.product_name
ORDER BY 3 DESC
LIMIT 10;`

## What are the industries with the highest contribution to carbon emissions?
Top 5 ngành thải ra khí carbon nhiều nhất

SQL: 
`SELECT i.industry_group, sum(p.carbon_footprint_pcf) AS CO2_emissions
FROM product_emissions p
JOIN industry_groups i
ON p.industry_group_id = i.id
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5;`

| industry_group                     | CO2_emissions | 
| ---------------------------------: | ------------: | 
| Electrical Equipment and Machinery | 9801558       | 
| Automobiles & Components           | 2582264       | 
| Materials                          | 577595        | 
| Technology Hardware & Equipment    | 363776        | 
| Capital Goods                      | 258712        | 

**Insight:** Đứng đầu là ngành công nghiệp điện, hầu hết những ngành gây ô nhiễm môi trường đều đến từ điện và ngành công nghiệp sản xuất.

## What is the trend of carbon footprints (PCFs) over the years?
Các sản phẩm thải ra nhiều nhất trong năm 2015

SQL: 
`SELECT p.product_name, com.company_name, cou.country_name, i.industry_group,
       sum(p.carbon_footprint_pcf) AS CO2_emissions
FROM product_emissions as p
JOIN industry_groups as i ON p.industry_group_id = i.id
JOIN companies as com ON p.company_id = com.id
JOIN countries as cou ON p.country_id = cou.id	
WHERE year = 2015
GROUP BY 1,2,3,4
ORDER BY 5 DESC;`

## Which industry groups has demonstrated the most notable decrease in carbon footprints (PCFs) over time?
Các ngành hàng giảm thải khí carbon

SQL: 
`SELECT industry_group,
       sum(case when year = 2013 then carbon_footprint_pcf end) AS CO2_emissions_2013,
	   sum(case when year = 2017 then carbon_footprint_pcf end) AS CO2_emissions_2017
FROM product_emissions as p
JOIN industry_groups as i ON p.industry_group_id = i.id
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 2 DESC;`
